data.description: ****BRAND NEW TO THE MARKET**** This nice very clean, 5 bedroom 3 bath home is one that you must see. Newer architectural roof, vinyl windows, and vinyl siding for a low maintenance exterior. This home sits in a quiet nice neighborhood. The kitchen has a charming feel to it with the nice oak cabinets, tile backsplash and all appliances are included. The dining area combined with the kitchen would be the best place to entertain friends and family. With a living room upstairs and a finished family room downstairs, this listing is one that should not be passed up. The landscaping has alot of mature trees and flower beds to complete the whole package. See it today.
